    <title>【医史】朱元璋之子朱橚曾参与编写《救荒本草》 影响明清一批自然科学家</title>
    <link href="/2025/05/06/%E3%80%90%E5%8C%BB%E5%8F%B2%E3%80%91%E6%9C%B1%E5%85%83%E7%92%8B%E4%B9%8B%E5%AD%90%E6%9C%B1%E6%A9%9A%E6%9B%BE%E5%8F%82%E4%B8%8E%E7%BC%96%E5%86%99%E3%80%8A%E6%95%91%E8%8D%92%E6%9C%AC%E8%8D%89%E3%80%8B-%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E6%98%8E%E6%B8%85%E4%B8%80%E6%89%B9%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6%E5%AE%B6/"/>
